            "id": 6426969,
            "title": "外資近5日賣超個股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>1. 外資累計賣超 5 日的股票<br/>主動統一台股增長 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00981A:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00981A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00981A-TW</a>)、主動元大AI新經濟 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00990A:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00990A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00990A-TW</a>)、群益證 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6005:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6005\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6005-TW</a>)、主動群益科技創新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00992A:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00992A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00992A-TW</a>)、元大台灣50正2 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00631L:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00631L\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00631L-TW</a>)</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>2. 外資累計賣超 4 日的股票<br/>友達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2409-TW</a>)、主動統一台股增長 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00981A:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00981A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00981A-TW</a>)、旺宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2337:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2337\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2337-TW</a>)、群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)、富邦科技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0052:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0052\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0052-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>3. 外資累計賣超 3 日的股票<br/>友達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2409-TW</a>)、群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)、主動統一台股增長 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00981A:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00981A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00981A-TW</a>)、台玻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1802:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1802-TW</a>)、元大台灣50 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0050:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Arti